Speech Assistant AAC - Privacy Policy
This privacy policy is provided by ASoft, the developer of the app Speech Assistant AAC.
•
The app does not collect or share any kind of personal or other information.
•
The conversations always stay private.
•
The app does not need an internet connection to function.
Permissions
For some functions the app needs permissions to function correctly.
•
Photos/Media/Files
Used to access the file system to give the user the possibility to create a backup file and to restore a backup file.
•
In-app purchases
Used for the in app purchase for the upgrade to the full version of the app.
Information
For more information or questions please mail to
info@asoft.nl
or visit
www.asoft.nl
This policy was last modified on 22-12-2021.